  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA53">
<l>cīrārnta koṉṟai malartaḻaippac cēṇulavi</l>
<l>nīrārnta pēriyāṟu nīttamāyp - pērārnta</l>
<l>nāṇpāmpu koṇṭacaitta nammīcaṉ poṉmuṭitāṉ</l>
<l>kāṇpārkkuc cevvēyōr kār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The golden crown of our lord that is tied with the snake as a string that is filled</l>
<l>with grandeur, there being the flood of the great river filled with water spreading</l>
<l>far, while the blossoms of the Laburnum filled with excellence thrive,</l>
<l>is rightly a rainy season for those who see it.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
